NXEngine for DC
===============

About
-----

Port of NxEngine to the Dreamcast

NxEngine is a complete open-source clone/rewrite of the Cave Story.

Original NXEngine website http://nxengine.sourceforge.net 



Installation
------------
windows user try ready to burn iso

unix user try burn script
you should to install cdrkit

unzip data.zip

ubzip raw.zip

unzip binary

IP.BIN data raw

put 1st_read.bin data

before excute the script 
edit dev_option

type 
$ wodim --devices

example
dev_option="/dev/sg4"

finary 
$ sh burm.sh

Controls
--------

Dreamcast controller:
D-pad:	left,right,down,up
Start:	MENU(F3)

thease buttons and triggers are not assigned in default
A,B,X,Y,L trigger,R trigger


Dreamcast keyboard:
arrow:	left,right,down,up
F3:	MENU
Z:		jump
X:		fire
Q:		inventory
W:		mapsystem
A:	prev wepon
S:	next wepon


